data.value:
Alaska Fortified Ready-to-Drink Milk 170mL is a convenient and nutritious beverage designed to support children's growth and development. Enriched with essential nutrients, it provides both strength and mental sharpness in a ready-to-drink format.
Type of Milk: UHT-Processed Fortified Milk Drink
Ideal For: Children aged 3 and above, and adults seeking a nutritious, ready-to-drink milk option
Ingredients: Water Reconstituted milk Sugar Stabilizers, and added vitamins and minerals including Protein Iron Calcium Choline Iodine
Where to buy: SM Supermarket Quezon, Puregold Pasay
______________________________________________________________________________
Nutritional Information (per 170ml serving) Calories: 125 kcal
Total Fat: 6g
Carbohydrates: 12g
Protein: 5g
